Ezulwini Consensus bụ ọnọdụ na mmekọrịta mba ụwa na mgbanwe nke United Nations, nke African Union kwenyere
Ọ na-akpọ oku maka ndị nnọchiteanya na ndị ọchịchị onye kwuo uche ya, nke Africa, dị ka mpaghara ụwa ndị ọzọ niile, na-anọchite anya ya.
.. Nkwekọrịta ahụ bụ aha Ezulwini, ndagwurugwu dị n'etiti Eswatini (nke a na-akpọ Swaziland n'oge ahu), bụ ebe e mere nkwekọrịta ahụ na 2005.
A nabatara nkwenye ahụ na nnọkọ pụrụ iche nke Council Executive of the African Union, na Maachị 2005, na Addis Ababa.
Nkwekọrịta ahụ kpuchiri ọtụtụ ebe, gụnyere: EXECUTIVE COUNCIL, 7th Extraordinary Session (7-8 March 2005)
Ọnọdụ CommON AFRICAN n'elu ihe mgbochi nke mba UNITED: "THE EZULWINI CONSENSUS" (Report)
